      <title>墨西哥要求秘鲁人签证以打击移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-to-require-visas-for-peruvians-in-migration-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥将要求秘鲁人获得签证才能进入该国，以阻止来自南美国家的移民流量“大幅增加”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-to-require-visas-for-peruvians-in-migration-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和法国呼吁在华盛顿访问之前向乌克兰提供更多援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uk-france-call-for-more-ukraine-aid-ahead-of-washington-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦在访问华盛顿之前警告称，“未能支持乌克兰的代价”，敦促美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊找到国会批准一项 600 亿美元军事援助计划的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uk-france-call-for-more-ukraine-aid-ahead-of-washington-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥就厄瓜多尔突袭大使馆事件提出抗议，寻求联合国裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔警方冲进墨西哥驻厄瓜多尔大使馆逮捕一名寻求庇护的高级政客后，墨西哥将向联合国正式起诉厄瓜多尔，两国关系急转直下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/mexico-seeks-un-ruling-in-protest-of-ecuador-s-raid-of-embassy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在海上的大规模建设令菲律宾在小岛的扩张相形见绌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南海的一个小岛象征着这场斗争——和差距——与中国相比，菲律宾在争议水域主张其权利的努力，中国对大部分水域拥有主权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/china-s-huge-sea-buildup-dwarfs-philippine-push-on-tiny-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>医生短缺造成的死亡加剧了韩国的选举焦虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/deaths-from-doctor-shortage-fuel-election-angst-in-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023 年 3 月，韩国大邱市一名 17 岁女孩从一栋大楼坠落，救护车被三家缺乏医生救治的医院拒之门外后死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/deaths-from-doctor-shortage-fuel-election-angst-in-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>图斯克的联盟赢得波兰地方选举以增强权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/tusk-s-coalition-wins-local-elections-in-poland-to-bolster-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·图斯克总理领导的执政联盟有望赢得波兰地方选举，这对于他的四个月政府来说是一场苦乐参半的胜利，该政府寻求修复与欧盟的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/tusk-s-coalition-wins-local-elections-in-poland-to-bolster-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 19:58:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登盟友反对停止美国向以色列转让武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统的一位参议院盟友表示，美国应继续向以色列提供武器，他拒绝了众议院议员的呼吁，即在对以色列导弹袭击导致加沙七名世界中央厨房援助人员死亡的事件进行全面调查之前暂停武器转让。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/biden-ally-opposes-halting-us-weapons-transfers-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多为加拿大人工智能行业推出 18 亿美元一揽子计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/trudeau-unveils-1-8-billion-plan-to-boost-ai-sector-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多继续在新预算之前发布支出公告，加拿大正在启动一项基金来促进其人工智能行业的发展，并创建一个新的人工智能安全研究所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/trudeau-unveils-1-8-billion-plan-to-boost-ai-sector-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 15:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗将释放因间谍罪入狱六年的四名活动人士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/iran-to-release-four-activists-jailed-for-spying-after-six-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四名因安全罪名入狱的伊朗环保活动人士的律师表示，他们将在入狱六年多后获释。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/iran-to-release-four-activists-jailed-for-spying-after-six-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡称胜利临近，从加沙撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/war-in-middle-east-israel-has-responses-ready-for-iran-scenarios</link>
      <description><![CDATA[军方官员周日表示，以色列正在从加沙南部的汗尤尼斯撤出部分部队，并称随着针对哈马斯的战争进入六个月大关，以色列已经结束了在那里的任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/war-in-middle-east-israel-has-responses-ready-for-iran-scenarios</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:48:26 GMT</pubDate>
